WEBVTT

01:04.233 --> 01:06.333
Come on. Quickly!

11:50.666 --> 11:54.000
And what is your name?

11:54.233 --> 11:56.200
This is Victoria.

11:57.166 --> 12:01.100
I think she is the daughter
of a Mushkegowuk woman,

12:01.100 --> 12:04.200
but she was captured
by Europeans long ago.

12:04.700 --> 12:08.766
She has been forced to serve white men,
to lay with white men.

12:34.600 --> 12:37.633
The Europeans are not content
with our trade,

12:37.633 --> 12:40.333
now they take our people, our girls.

12:41.200 --> 12:44.400
What would you have us do?

12:46.300 --> 12:47.400
Raise a group of fighters.

12:48.233 --> 12:52.400
Set them to free the people,
one fort at a time.

12:53.633 --> 13:02.300
Sokanon,
what you ask will end in bloodshed.

13:02.566 --> 13:08.033
There will be bloodshed
no matter what we do. We must act.

13:11.066 --> 13:14.166
We must discuss this.

13:58.600 --> 14:03.233
If you don't mind, the lady would like
the comfort of your weapon.

14:03.666 --> 14:05.400
Thank you.

18:44.333 --> 18:47.000
We have conditions.

18:47.000 --> 18:52.266
The first is that there must be
no more bloodshed than is necessary.

18:53.200 --> 18:59.033
And you, Sokanon, must lead the party.

19:01.100 --> 19:07.433
We have seen first-hand
Sokanon's skill and knowledge.

19:07.433 --> 19:12.666
We can agree to this. She will lead.

19:13.500 --> 19:18.466
We can provide you with men,

19:18.466 --> 19:22.000
but you must provide
the necessary resources.

19:22.400 --> 19:24.500
I understand.

19:26.066 --> 19:27.566
Where will you go?

30:16.300 --> 30:18.600
How many pelts can we take?

30:19.166 --> 30:20.366
Now?

30:20.700 --> 30:22.266
Two boats.

30:22.500 --> 30:25.000
In a few days, we could move them all.

30:25.300 --> 30:26.666
We don't have a few days.

30:27.133 --> 30:28.733
Two boats.

33:32.533 --> 33:34.200
Wonderful.

34:17.766 --> 34:21.699
Gentlemen, pack up your things.
Let's get out of here.

34:54.199 --> 35:02.033
There is a battalion of Redcoats
moving through the river valley.

35:02.033 --> 35:07.100
They will be here soon.

40:32.566 --> 40:34.566
You've made your choice.
